									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="The mission is to rescue the 7 crew members of the Atlas Bravo, as well as eliminate/capture 2 Syndikat leaders in the area who may be responsible.<br/><br/>   " \n "Additionally, we should help the HIDF clear out key target locations on the SE of the mainland.<br/><br/>   " \n "The HIDF have sent out a task force to hit some of these target locations but they were ambushed in route and require assistance.";
